And much prettier.
<SYNC Start=2051959><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2052109><P Class=EGCC>
Everything's changing, isn't it?
<SYNC Start=2054552><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2054702><P Class=EGCC>
The whole country is getting richer.<br>
