And Florrie, of course ...
<SYNC Start=2067371><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2067521><P Class=EGCC>
Mind you, she couldn't really've<br>
stayed, poor little thing.
<SYNC Start=2070841><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2071851><P Class=EGCC>
Only mrs. Perkins and Wilson left.
<SYNC Start=2074879><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2075029><P Class=EGCC>
You keep our bodies and souls<br>
alive somehow, don't you, my darling?
<SYNC Start=2079334><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2080675><P Class=EGCC>
Such a struggle...
<SYNC Start=2083747><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2084588><P Class=EGCC>
How about Roger paying his rent?<br>
