<SYNC Start=2113006><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2113156><P Class=EGCC>
As long as we can find our way out.
<SYNC Start=2115616><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2115766><P Class=EGCC>
Claude has a little jungle, don't you Claude?<br>
Full of poisonous orquids.
<SYNC Start=2119832><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2119982><P Class=EGCC>
Orquids? How lovely.<br>
