<SYNC Start=2219337><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2219487><P Class=EGCC>
Vanished?
<SYNC Start=2221400><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2221550><P Class=EGCC>
You can blame me for that.
<SYNC Start=2223855><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2224005><P Class=EGCC>
