<SYNC Start=2404421><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2404571><P Class=EGCC>
As soon as he saw a woman,<br>
He couldn't help himself.
<SYNC Start=2407278><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
