<SYNC Start=2415741><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2415891><P Class=EGCC>
Did he chase you?
<SYNC Start=2418126><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2418276><P Class=EGCC>
