<SYNC Start=2436233><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2436383><P Class=EGCC>
You ought really be inside, you know?
<SYNC Start=2438712><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2438862><P Class=EGCC>
I've got Roger's coat.<br>
