<SYNC Start=2442492><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2442642><P Class=EGCC>
Come along, then.<br>
Good night, ladies.
<SYNC Start=2445695><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2458127><P Class=EGCC>
Thank you, Moira.
<SYNC Start=2460108><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2465401><P Class=EGCC>
Well, it's obvious, isn't it? Jack's<br>
a monster. So,
<SYNC Start=2469865><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
