<SYNC Start=2500558><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2500708><P Class=EGCC>
But you must be aware of distractions.
<SYNC Start=2503599><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2504309><P Class=EGCC>
Distractions?
<SYNC Start=2506273><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2534656><P Class=EGCC>
Come.
<SYNC Start=2536356><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2536862><P Class=EGCC>
I'll get another bat.
<SYNC Start=2539141><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2541894><P Class=EGCC>
You know what happened, don't you?<br>
- Sorry?
<SYNC Start=2545160><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2545310><P Class=EGCC>
With Castairs. Don't you?
<SYNC Start=2547754><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2552495><P Class=EGCC>
Come on, partner.
<SYNC Start=2554618><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2560206><P Class=EGCC>
Wait a minute.
<SYNC Start=2562105><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2563106><P Class=EGCC>
Just like ...
<SYNC Start=2565928><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2568607><P Class=EGCC>
Wha-- Robert!<br>
