<SYNC Start=2571661><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2571811><P Class=EGCC>
brought madam's clothes, madam.
<SYNC Start=2574200><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2574491><P Class=EGCC>
Perhaps you'd like to take it<br>
to Miss Marple, please, Robert.
<SYNC Start=2577680><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2577691><P Class=EGCC>
Mind you, where will I find<br>
Miss Marple, madam?
<SYNC Start=2579633><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2580622><P Class=EGCC>
I'll show you.
<SYNC Start=2583194><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2583344><P Class=EGCC>
Come on.
<SYNC Start=2585362><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2586929><P Class=EGCC>
Might I inquire if madam would need<br>
some help with the bat, madam?
<SYNC Start=2590967><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2601859><P Class=EGCC>
Missed a bit.<br>
It's a nice moustache,..
<SYNC Start=2605221><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2605371><P Class=EGCC>
